column5: The family of WC has been huge in helping me put together my first trip to Canada. The truck and boat are packed, the gear is stowed and the guys are restless!!! To all those who answered a question, shared some input, gave of your time in the chat room or stoked my excitement... Thank you.
Have a blast! I know I will in three weeks.
Keek, Be sure to post a report on your trip and fishing when you get back. Rich B
keek:Have a great trip and would like to hear about your trip when you get back. Remember Rule #1: Don't leave fish to find fish. Best.
Have a great trip..we will be right behind you...leaving in 7 hours for Cedar Lake in Perrault Falls..cant wait...cant sleep..

Glenman, Be sure to post how you did......our group had a great time a few weeks ago at Cedar Lake Lodge, though the weather (lightning) shut us down for a day and 1/2. Hope you and your friends have a great week.....we're heading back up the 3rd week of Sept for the fall bite. Rich B
we will be there the next week.
Be safe and have a great trip. Will be watching for the report when you return
